# J1 Motors WMS Enterprise Deployment

Upload the CONTENTS of this folder to the GitHub repository root.

Required files visible at repository root:

- package.json
- package-lock.json
- netlify.toml
- vite.config.ts
- tsconfig.json
- src/
- public/
- supabase/

Netlify environment variables:

- VITE_SUPABASE_URL
- VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY

Build command: npm run build
Publish directory: dist
